customize_plugin_tips: Customize path and parameters of plugin, default file path is client plugins directory.
customize_plugin_tips_sip003: Customize path and parameters of SIP003 standard plugin, default file path is client plugins directory.
only_for_server_groups: Only for the subscription server groups (right click on the server groups then function menu will pop up)
polling_tips: Select node one by one to send request
random_tips: Select node at random to send request
readme: checkout plugins installation instructions on github readme page
readme_acl: Modifying ACL (Access Control List) configuration and then back to home page, proxy server will reload automatically, you can checkout ACL instructions on github readme page (Note: ACL is not suitable for SSR server)
please_confirm_v2ray-plugin_installed_on: The v2ray-plugin has been built-in, there is nothing to do. If you prefer to use external v2ray-plugin, put it into client plugins directory or create a soft link to there with command [ln -s].
please_confirm_kcptun_installed_on_your_: Must install kcptun first, check more details on github readme page. After downloading this plugin, rename it to kcptun, finally put it into plugins directory. For Linux/Mac users remember to give it permission with command [chmod].
not_applicable_to_linux_snap_application: not applicable to linux snap version
recover_pac_file_with_link: Recover the pac file using the gfw-list link below
recover_pac_file_with_file: Recover the pac file using the local gfw-list file
failed_to_update_subscription: Fail to update subscription group info
server_url_not_set: Remote server URL is not found, please remove the subscription server group and try add it again.
pac_port_tips: Port where PAC file is served
restart_when_changed: Proxy server will reload when back to home page
restart_pac_tips: PAC server will reload when back to home page. And you might need to restart your web browsers for PAC rules to take effect
customize_global_pac_tips: The global rules will be covered when use 'GFWLIST URL' to re-generate PAC file, usually it's recommended to customize user rules.
gfwlist_url_tips: GFWList file used to generate PAC
load_balance_tips: Client will try to connect multiple servers and disperse traffic pressure to each server
plugins_dir_tips: The external plugins (such as v2ray-plugin/kcptun) should be placed in this directory.
import_server_subscription_from_clipboar: Import Subscription Server Group From Clipboard
HTTP(S) url that used to download multiple ss(r) config data, data will be parsed and import by client. The supported cloud platforms: paofu,monocloud,fast-frog(not recommended)...
the_recovery_is_failed: The recovery is failed! please confirm whether the file format is json
reset_all_data_tips: This action will reset all data to its defaults.
sure_to_delete_task_tips: Are you sure to delete this task?
sure_to_delete_runner_tips: Are you sure to delete this workflow? all task scripts will lost.
fail_to_load_workflow_demo_script: Fail to load workflow demo script
